eu.cqse.check.framework.typetracker

Class TypeInfoExtractorBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.framework.typetracker.TypeInfoExtractorBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITypeInfoExtractor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbapTypeInfoExtractor, CLikeTypeInfoExtractorBase

    public abstract class TypeInfoExtractorBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITypeInfoExtractor
    An abstract base class for type info extractors. This base class implements the ITypeInfoExtractor.extract(ShallowEntity)-method and passes the given entity to a method corresponding to the entity's type. Subclasses must implement these type-specific methods
